    Dumb Moments in Dumb Advertising with Dumb Garmin    </a> </h3><small>by Johnny Debacle<br></small>
  <div class="entrybody">
    <p><center><img src="http://longorshortcapital.com/new_nuvifone.jpg"/></center></p>
<p>Have you heard the news?  Garmin&#8217;s (NASDAQ: <a href="http://finance.yahoo.com/q?s=grmn">GRMN</a>) new nuvifone is new?</p>
